programme.title: The World's Greatest Painters - Season 1 - Edgar Degas
programme.desc: Edgar Degas was a French painter born in 1834 in Paris and passed out in 1917 in the same city. He was officially known as an impressionist painter, but he didn’t join them in many features. The artist explored all genre and artistic themes, but the landscapes were one of his weaknesses. Dance was one of his favourite subjects and it will mark his career with paintings still famous nowadays. In 1855 he joined the Beaux-Arts in Paris to learn but he preferred to follow the approach of the great classical masters of the Italian Renaissance and went to Italia to deepen his art. Unfortunately, in 1860 his vision started to deteriorate and in 1905 he retreated into his studio, embittered by the blindness that won on him. Most of his works were auctioned the following year.

programme.title: Within the frame - Season 1 - Napoleon
programme.desc: An emblematic figure in Europe at the turn of the 18th century, this corporal who became Emperor of France unleashed the imagination of artists from whom he commissioned many works. Discover the victorious young “Bonaparte at the Pont d’Arcole” immortalised by the Antoine-Jean Gros in 1796. Observe also the portraits of all the guests present during the “Coronation of Napoleon” and his triumphant gesture as he crowned his wife Josephine in David’s masterpiece displayed in the Louvre Museum. - Enjoy your visit!

programme.title: Art quiz - Episode 58
programme.desc: Test and develop your artistic culture with Art Quiz, the game that will allow you to become unaware of art. Whether it's artists, works of art, artistic trends, the price of works... nothing will be a secret for you anymore. Now it's your turn to play!

programme.desc: Raphael Federici (street artist), Marine Goodmorning (illustrator), Luca Fiore (cartoonist) and Harry Boudchicha (drawing teacher) reveal their best drawing techniques. programme.desc: In this episode, we will discuss with Pierre Terrasson, photographer. He is considered the rock, punk and new wave photographer of the 1980s, but not only. He started to get interested in photography at the age of 14-15 with his friends. He will tell us how he became a photographer and talk about his life, his career, and what made him famous.

programme.title: The decisive moment - Season 2 - Henri Dauman, part 1
programme.desc: In this episode we will meet Henri Dauman, photographer. He emigrated to the United States in 1950 and became a journalist. He collaborated with all the major American and European titles. Through his snapshots of Andy Warhol, Brigitte Bardot, Elvis Presley, or Marilyn Monroe, for recognized newspapers, his priority remains to tell stories.

programme.title: Art News - Season - Botero, the sacred Colombian monster
programme.desc: It was in the city of Medellín that the man who claims to be the most Colombian of Colombian artists grew up and drew his inspiration. Medellín, the stronghold of Pablo Escobar, is a concentration of Colombia, both tragic and exuberant, which Botero soon left for Europe, but which remains inseparable from his style.

programme.sub-title: The dawn of pop art - In the eye of Fernand Léger
programme.desc: Fernand Leger combines modernity and dynamism in his works. To exhibit his art, he has a museum dedicated to him in Biot. Let's have a look at the impressive collection of this museum, surrounded by a superb park laid out by Henri Fisch. You will be able to discover the artist, he was at the same time a painter, a ceramist, a sculptor, a draughtsman, a creator of tapestries and stained glass. Through the various periods leading him from post impressionism to pop art through cubism, the artist asserts himself as one of the most prolific and original artists of the 20th century.

programme.sub-title: Giacometti, between tradition and avant-garde at the Musée Maillol

This exhibition shows how Giacometti evolved from style to style. It tells his story from the first busts he sculpted at the age of 13, to the realization of large-scale sculptures towards the end of his life.

programme.desc: He experimented with a technique that would later be described as pointillist. He juxtaposed fine complementary touches of paint, seeking purity and luminosity. There are a few bluish, rounded reflections in the orange, giving it relief by simply sketching out the details.

programme.desc: Private Tour takes you to the discovery of the exhibition "Dancing Gross" at LaM in Villeneuve d'Ascq, the museum of modern, contemporary and raw art. This exhibition presents works made by artists, dancers or not, and questions the themes of gesture and movement. It can be a simple photograph immortalizing a movement, a dance, or even reproductions of merry-go-rounds which will remind you the period of childhood.

programme.title: Private Tour - Season 1 - I have the right to have rights
programme.sub-title: I have the right to have rights
programme.desc: Private Tour takes you to discover the exhibitions on human rights at the Musée de l'Homme in Paris. Nine street artists invaded the walls of the atrium to illustrate articles of the Universal Declaration of Human Rights. It is a unique exhibition because the artists came on site and realized their works in front of the public. Let's discover these engaged and unconventional artistic creations.

programme.title: Pop art
programme.desc: From the birth of a unique voice in the artworld of the sixties, to worldwide consecration in the 90’s and 2000’s… From the “Ecole des Beaux Arts” in Paris to the Grand Prize of Rome, going all the way through Italy’s Villa Medicis and the Hermitage Museum in Saint Petersburg… André Brasilier is a self-defined “transfigurative” French painter, seeking harmony between plastic construction and emotion, and drawing his inspiration from life itself. As he is nearing his 100th birthday, this exclusive documentary invites you to step through a retrospective celebrating 70 years of a unique career, which is held at the Hangaram Design Museum of Seoul, South Korea.

programme.title: Art investigation - Season 1 - Autumn - Manet
programme.desc: This documentary traces the history of one of Edouard Manet's last works, "L'Automne", an unfinished masterpiece, now kept in the Musée des Beaux-Arts in Nancy. At the end of his life, Edouard Manet embarked on a pictorial project on the theme of the four seasons. To represent "Autumn", the painter chose Méry Laurent as his model. We look at this young woman of modest origins, sold at the age of 15 by her mother to the governor of the city of Nancy. She quickly became the mistress of Dr. Evans, Napoleon III's very rich dentist, and saw a whole artistic world open up to her. Méry Laurent visits the studio of Édouard Manet, who is already famous for his scandalous paintings. The young woman immediately falls under the artist's spell and becomes one of his favourite models... The investigation continues the trail of the other paintings in the 4 seasons series. First to the Thyssen Museum in Madrid to try to unravel the mystery of "The Amazon", a painting that could well represent "Summer”. And then to New York, behind the scenes of an exceptional auction at Christie's of "Spring", estimated at 32 million dollars.

programme.title: Ride your Dream
programme.desc: El motociclismo era un mundo de hombres. Hasta ahora. Este documental nos descubre a la española Ana Carrasco, la primera piloto en ganar un campeonato del mundo y que ha revolucionado el ámbito de las dos ruedas. A través de conversaciones con su familia y equipo, conoceremos las motivaciones de Ana, con qué obstáculos se ha encontrado y qué sueños sigue persiguiendo. Su carrera, desde sus orígenes en un pueblo de Murcia hasta el triunfo del campeonato mundial, su sueño desde pequeña, es una fuente de inspiración para cualquiera. Ella misma es un claro ejemplo de lucha y superación cuya historia, llena de emoción, anima a que todos luchemos por nuestros sueños.

programme.title: Episodios 5-6
programme.desc: Bola de partido | Una noche europea

programme.title: Los secretos de La Roja – Campeones del mundo
programme.desc: El 11 de julio de 2010, la Selección Española de Fútbol consiguió su ansiada primera Copa del Mundo. La victoria fue el triunfo de un equipo, pero también el de un país entero. Aun así, dentro de este exitoso suceso hay pequeñas historias de esfuerzo y superación que subrayan el carácter de un equipo que estaba destinado a ser leyenda. La selección llegó a Sudáfrica con Vicente del Bosque liderando el equipo y con el reciente triunfo de la Eurocopa de 2008, pero el favoritismo atribuido a “La Roja” pronto generó desconfianza y dudas con la derrota ante Suiza en el primer partido del mundial. No obstante, consiguieron salir adelante gracias al buen fútbol y a un claro objetivo: hacer historia

programme.title: Episodios 9-10
programme.desc: Hora de decir adiós | Último capítulo

programme.title: Break Point: a Davis Cup Story
programme.desc: Dieciocho equipos lucharán para levantar la preciada ensaladera. La España de Rafa Nadal es una de las favoritas, pero pronto sufre un duro revés: el número dos del equipo, Roberto Bautista, debe abandonar la competición y volver a su Castellón natal para acompañar a su padre en sus últimas horas de vida. Sin Bautista, Nadal y Feliciano López consiguen llevar al equipo hasta la final de forma heroica. Y entonces salta la noticia que emociona al mundo del deporte: tras el funeral de su padre, Bautista vuelve a la competición y decide jugar. Juntos de nuevo, los integrantes del equipo español tratarán de asaltar una gran final en la que está en juego algo que va mucho más allá del tenis.

programme.title: Ettore Bassi: Stage and Race
programme.desc: El actor italiano Ettore Bassi es muy conocido por su trabajo en cine, televisión y teatro. No todos saben que también es piloto profesional de carreras de montaña. Hoy su vida se suele dividir entre sus dos pasiones en dos contextos muy distintos: el escenario o la pista de carreras. En 2022, las dos realidades colisionan cuando lo contratan simultáneamente para una actuación y una carrera, cada una en una punta de Italia. Bassi decide dedicarse a ambos proyectos que le apasionan, sabiendo que tener éxito es casi imposible. En esta elección y en su determinación se revela mucho sobre este hombre y sobre su pasado...

programme.title: Give Up Tomorrow
programme.desc: En Filipinas, un hombre inocente se enfrenta a la pena de muerte en un caso de asesinato controvertido que separó dos familias y una nación entera.

programme.title: About Heaven
programme.desc: Filmmaker Stéphane Goel goes out in search of answers about the existence of an idyllic place after death. Several Swiss in the fall of their lives, whether they are believers or atheists, tell us what they think about this idea.

programme.title: One Day After Peace
programme.desc: Robi Damelin perdió a su hijo menor David a causa de la bala de un francotirador palestino mientras manejaba un puesto de control militar en Cisjordania. Al principio, Robi trató de contactar al asesino de su hijo, que ahora está cumpliendo condena en una prisión israelí. Ella quería iniciar un diálogo con él y sus padres, pero el palestino se negó. Después de todo, explicó, su hijo era parte de las fuerzas del ejército de Ocupación que negaba a su pueblo su soberanía. Sin inmutarse, Robi decidió regresar a Sudáfrica para ver cómo el país donde nació se había embarcado en una búsqueda para lograr el perdón y la reconciliación después de décadas de apartheid.

programme.title: SEVE - Artista, Luchador, Leyenda
programme.desc: Seve sigue siendo una leyenda, un gran campeón, el hombre responsable de convertir la Ryder Cup moderna en la gran oportunidad que es. Su pasión por el golf era tal que de niño se colaba en el campo para jugar de noche y de mayor seguía haciéndolo para "encontrar la magia". Los miembros de su familia, su círculo cercano, otros grandes deportistas y él mismo cuentan su historia en este nuevo material inédito. Una fascinante historia sobre el talento, la confianza y el valor: la vida de Seve... y su partida.

programme.title: 265 días sin olas
programme.desc: Una historia extraordinaria a la par que única sobre cómo un grupo de surferos locales consiguió crear una comunidad y una cultura de surf contra todo pronóstico en un litoral con poco más de 100 días de olas al año. Analizamos la evolución del surf a través de las personas, junto con el cambio socioeconómico exponencial que ha tenido lugar en Barcelona y sus alrededores desde los años 60 hasta el presente. Entre los apasionados e intrépidos protagonistas, hablamos con los dos pioneros que sentaron las bases de esta cultura y con representantes de la nueva generación que han vivido y crecido con el surf de forma totalmente distinta.

programme.title: Discovering Canary Islands - Episodio 1- 2
programme.desc: Episodio 1 - Lanzarote | Episodio 2 - Fuerteventura

programme.title: Corumbiara
programme.desc: Corumbiara: ¿Disparan a los indios, no? El cineasta Vicent Carelli estaba en el área desarrollando su proyecto Video in Villages con comunidades indígenas en el oeste de Brasil cuando recibió una llamada de un activista informándole de una masacre ocurrida en el municipio de Corumbiara. Allí, los terratenientes y los empresarios madereros atacaron a una comunidad indígena que se negó a ser desplazada de sus tierras. La cámara de Carelli se convierte en la única arma que los activistas tenían a mano para recolectar evidencia de la masacre, imágenes que salieron a la luz para comenzar un controvertido proceso judicial que finalmente falló a favor de los terratenientes.

programme.title: Future My Love
programme.desc: Al borde de perder el amor idealista de su vida, la cineasta Maja Borg nos lleva en un poético viaje por el colapso financiero, explorando un modelo económico y social radicalmente diferente propuesto por el futurista de 95 años Jacque Fresco. ¿Cuánta libertad estamos dispuestos a dar a los que amamos? ¿Y cuánta responsabilidad estamos dispuestos a asumir por nuestra sociedad? Tejiendo cuidadosamente una textura de material de archivo, película Super 8 en blanco y negro, y HD en color, Borg representa de manera conmovedora la lucha universal entre nuestras cabezas y corazones en tiempos de grandes cambios.

programme.title: I Am Breathing
programme.desc: A medida que su cuerpo se debilita, su perspectiva de la vida cambia. Sabiendo que sólo le quedan unos pocos meses de vida, y mientras todavía tiene la capacidad de hablar, Neil prepara una carta y una caja de recuerdos para su hijo pequeño Oscar y comunica su experiencia y sus pensamientos sobre la vida en un blog - y en esta película que estaba decidido a hacer.

programme.title: Everyone Wants To Be The Next Weismann
programme.desc: Tras vivir a la sombra de su último descubrimiento, un coleccionista de arte intenta encontrar a su próximo gran artista, un pintor taiwanés residente en Brookling. ¿Será la segunda parte tan buena o mejor que la primera?

programme.title: El mariachi gringo
programme.desc: A stifled, small-town man stuck in a dead end life, runs away to Mexico to be a mariachi singer. MARIACHI GRINGO is a musical tour-de-force exploring the reality of "following your dreams" across cultural, personal, social and geographical borders.

programme.title: La última noticia
programme.desc: A Peruvian radio host risks his life to report on clashes between police and militant guerrillas.

programme.title: Bendita rebeldía
programme.desc: Beatriz, a failed psychologist, flees to her childhood home to escape fraud charges, only to discover that her quirky aunt has turned the estate into a high school. What seems at first a terrible surprise will in fact help her finally find a fulfilling path in life as an unconventional theatre instructor.

programme.title: Recuperando a mi ex
programme.desc: A retired couple will have to defend their home against an unpredicted menace: Their kids moving back.

programme.title: Implacable
programme.desc: Max is a teenager who imagines himself as an implacable ladies man who can get any girl he wants. His life will take a 180º turn when he takes Dan, a smart, athletic and handsome twenty-something, under his wing and teaches him everything he knows. None of them imagined that this would make them compete for the affection of the same girl.

programme.title: La Sra. Haidi
programme.desc: One stormy night, a house near a little-traveled road. Mrs. Haidi lives there, alone in the company of her dogs. An accident on the road, a couple: Pablo and Mara, who seek help, but cannot imagine the nightmare they will experience that night. A psychological thriller that surprises every painting.

programme.title: Fuga de la Patagonia
programme.desc: Escape from Patagonia is a gaucho-western film set in the tumultuous Patagonia of late nineteenth century. It's a story of survival, based on real facts from the personal diary of the Argentinian pioneer Francisco P. Moreno.

programme.title: Como te ves, me vi
programme.desc: The story presents a dysfunctional family, whose problems are accentuated by the difficult relationship between a father and his adolescent son. Narrated in two timelines, present and past, the director reflects on adulthood to recall that the father once was also young.

programme.title: Ella es Ramona
programme.desc: Ramona is a fat woman with too much weight and barely any luck, her universe seems to be collapsing after a series of unfortunate events. But everything will soon get better thanks to some magical beetles she finds in a Tarot café.

programme.title: El elegido
programme.desc: A man named Jacques Mornard arrives in Mexico in 1940, claiming to be a Belgian who is fleeing the war in Europe to join his girlfriend, one of refugee Leon Trotsky's secretaries. But nobody knows that in reality this conventional and cheerful young man is in fact an agent of the Soviet Secret Service and has been sent to assassinate Trotsky.

programme.title: Bellas de noche
programme.desc: Portraits of a group of famous showgirls who started out in Mexico's burlesque culture during the disco era.

programme.title: La creciente
programme.desc: Matia, a marginal young man, escapes to an island in the River Paraná. In an uncomfortable atmosphere that is not his own, he tries to start a new life, but the tensions his arrival cause take him back to his criminal past and to the idea of having to flee in order to survive.

programme.title: 7 Soles
programme.desc: El Negro, a "pollero" hired to cross a group of undocumented immigrants to the United States, decides that this will be his last trip for the organization. He wants to get out of business. The chiefs suspect him and send a subaltern, "El Gavilán", to watch him. On the rugged crossing the polleros betrayed themselves, losing part of their human "cargo". The Negro escapes from his former partners and also from justice. El Gavilán returns unpunished to his work as a "hooker." Nothing stops the deadly machinery of human trafficking.

programme.title: Bendita rebeldía
programme.desc: Beatriz, a failed psychologist, flees to her childhood home to escape fraud charges, only to discover that her quirky aunt has turned the estate into a high school. What seems at first a terrible surprise will in fact help her finally find a fulfilling path in life as an unconventional theatre instructor.

programme.title: Chivas: la película
programme.desc: The greatest team in Mexico in the worst moment in its history, awakens with the arrival of its new pastor. Against everything, they show the world that greatness is not a result, it is a journey.

programme.title: La madrecita
programme.desc: A picturesque indigenous woman pretends to be a nun and experiences a series of entanglements with the convent authorities.

programme.title: Jóvenes y bellas
programme.desc: Furious that his daughter Raquel spends her life running go-karts, dancing and singing rock, Ricardo sends her camping with her friends. On a ranch next to the girls' camp, Rubén and his brothers Rafael, Roque and Raúl build a school commissioned by his father Gumaro Paz, who prohibits them from dealing with women.

programme.title: En peligro de muerte
programme.desc: Viruta and Capulina look for gold in the West, but are captured by Indians. With a metal detector and the flash of a camera they will have to win the respect of the Indians and save the attractive young women Lupita and Lolita.

programme.title: Lo que le pasó a Sansón
programme.desc: El vago Tin Tan y su celosa novia, la peinadora Lila, van al cine a ver "Sansón y Dalila". De regreso a casa Tin Tan sueña con que él es Sansón y Lila es Dalila. En el sueño, Sansón tiene amores con Miriam, pero cae hechizado por la belleza de Dalila, quien le roba la fuerza al cortarle el cabello. Sansón recupera su fuerza y se enfrenta al príncipe Arthur.

programme.title: Tonta, tonta, pero no tanto
programme.desc: India Maria decides to go live with a cousin in the Mexican capital to find a good job, but all kinds of complications arise.

programme.title: La flecha envenenada
programme.desc: A young orphan is attacked by Apaches and must pay her father's debts, since she may be dispossessed of her land.

programme.title: La edad de la tentación
programme.desc: Un grupo de jóvenes se rebela contra la sociedad. Con Gastón Santos.

programme.title: Santo contra Capulina
programme.desc: Capulina is a night-watchman in a warehouse, a perfect job for him. When some thieves break in and steal some crates, El Santo is after them because they are using the warehouse for diamond smuggling. Capulina hinders their capture. Then he decides that he will put on a wrestler's mask and help El Santo to capture the crooks.

programme.title: El grito de la muerte
programme.desc: A cowboy and his partner are involved in an action adventure wanting to obtain information about a stone figure of a woman crying.

programme.title: Si me han de matar mañana
programme.desc: La vida de un hombre cambia totalmente cuando encuentra a su hija, que había sido secuestrada años atrás por unos villanos.

programme.title: Rosario
programme.desc: Rosario y Carlos, esposos, forman parte parte de una compañía de teatro. En una escena de celos, ella debe disparar y matarlo. Carlos ha tenido una aventura con Zulma, otra actriz de la compañía, lo que no ha ocultado. La normalidad vuelve al matrimonio, y ese mismo día en la escena final del drama que representaban Rosario y Carlos, ella mata accidentalmente a su marido. Alguien cambio la pistola....

programme.title: Chabelo y Pepito detectives
programme.desc: A commander friend of Chabelo and Pepito asks them to help him discover a gang that kidnaps children. They accept and infiltrate the gang to discover that the villains are aliens.

programme.title: Misterios de ultratumba
programme.desc: El típico pacto que ¿quién nunca lo hizo o pensó en hacerlo?: dos doctores se prometen que el primero que muera regresará para contarle al otro los secretos del más allá. Uno de ellos muere y se inicia una vorágine de crimen y locura, que incluye posesiones, asesinatos y venganzas post-mórtem.

programme.title: Duro pero seguro
programme.desc: A taco vendor brings fortune to her clientele, so a television producer employs her to monopolize her luck.

programme.title: El ataúd del vampiro
programme.desc: Graverobbers stumble upon the tomb of a vampire, who turns them into zombies to do his bidding, which is to stalk and capture beautiful women.
